Package com.vmware.vcenter.compute

The com.vmware.vcenter.compute package provides interfaces for managing compute policies.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Policies
    The Policies interface provides methods to manage compute policies.
    PoliciesTypes
    Defines the data types of the Policies API service.

    Defines the type descriptors for the Policies API service.
